"_blank\">http://www.fate-go.jp/</a><br />\n<br />\n<strong>-官方twitter-</strong><br />\n<a href=\"http://twitter.com/fgoproject\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2Ffgoproject&d=NOp1Vkza2C8DAO0UI1TKxEkviAvgRC9mxyv2vFgVDqU%3D&h=41f03faa\" target=\"_blank\">http://twitter.com/fgoproject</a><br />\n<br />\n<strong>-遊戲WIKI-</strong><br />\n日文<br />\n<a href=\"http://grand_order.wicurio.com/index.php\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fgrand_order.wicurio.com%2Findex.php&d=NOp1Vkza2C8DAO0UI1TKxEkviAvgRC9mxyv2vFgVDqU%3D&h=5d650488\" target=\"_blank\">http://grand_order.wicurio.com/index.php</a><br />\n中文(台)<br />\n<a href=\"http://kazemai.github.io/fgo-vz/index.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fkazemai.github.io%2Ffgo-vz%2Findex.html&d=NOp1Vkza2C8DAO0UI1TKxEkviAvgRC9mxyv2vFgVDqU%3D&h=b60d4739\" target=\"_blank\">http://kazemai.github.io/fgo-vz/index.html</a><br />\n<br />\n<strong>-靈基素材、絆效率表-</strong><ins></ins><br />\n<a href=\"https://docs.google.com/spreadsheets/d/1TrfSDteVZnjUPz68rKzuZWZdZZBLqw03FlvEToOvqH0/htmlview?sle=true#\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fdocs.google.com%2Fspreadsheets%2Fd%2F1TrfSDteVZnjUPz68rKzuZWZdZZBLqw03FlvEToOvqH0%2Fhtmlview%3Fsle%3Dtrue%23&d=NOp1Vkza2C8DAO0UI1TKxEkviAvgRC9mxyv2vFgVDqU%3D&h=66e79af5\" target=\"_blank\">https://docs.google.com/spreadsheets/d/1TrfSDteVZnjUPz68rKzuZWZdZZBLqw03FlvEToOvqH0/htmlview?sle=true#</a><br />\n<br />\n<strong>-素材計算機-</strong><br />\n<a href=\"http://fgosimulator.webcrow.jp/Material/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Ffgosimulator.webcrow.jp%2FMaterial%2F&d=NOp1Vkza2C8DAO0UI1TKxEkviAvgRC9mxyv2vFgVDqU%3D&h=2c0298d2\" target=\"_blank\">http://fgosimulator.webcrow.jp/Material/</a><br />\n<br />\n<strong>-戒賭熱線-</strong><br />\nTEL: 183 4633<br />\n<img src=\"http://www.hkjc.com/responsible-gambling/images/footer_icon.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.hkjc.com%2Fresponsible-gambling%2Fimages%2Ffooter_icon.jpg&h=f8bd194a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<strong>-連登FGO區黑名單-</strong><br />\n1.長期良美(歐盟會長、法老王)<br />\n<a href=\"http://i.imgur.com/20lTYan.jpg\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fi.imgur.com%2F20lTYan.jpg&d=NOp1Vkza2C8DAO0UI1TKxEkviAvgRC9mxyv2vFgVDqU%3D&h=947e2c6a\" target=\"_blank\">http://i.imgur.com/20lTYan.jpg</a><br />\n<a href=\"http://i.imgur.com/0Jpj3XR.jpg\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fi.imgur.com%2F0Jpj3XR.jpg&d=NOp1Vkza2C8DAO0UI1TKxEkviAvgRC9mxyv2vFgVDqU%3D&h=c69cc920\" target=\"_blank\">http://i.imgur.com/0Jpj3XR.jpg</a><br />\n<a href=\"http://i.imgur.com/ogNh2TM.png?1\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fi.imgur.com%2FogNh2TM.png%3F1&d=NOp1Vkza2C8DAO0UI1TKxEkviAvgRC9mxyv2vFgVDqU%3D&h=58dcb11a\" target=\"_blank\">http://i.imgur.com/ogNh2TM.png?1</a><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">0課20五*以上</span></span><br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong>慎入慎盲</strong></span></span><br />\n<br />\n2.字智波帶土<br />\n(開台1符中限定)<br />\n<br />\n3.西田望見<br />\n梅林pickup，多次曬出梅林，<br />\n但聲明自己只係想抽積子，<br />\n直接貼圖傷害一眾梅林難民弱小心靈。<br />\n<br />\n4.平凡痴線佬<br />\n個個都準備8號 ALL IN CSOR<br />\n我好期待睇大家抽<br />\n祝人人8號中CSOR<br />\n利申 我果隻CSOR 陪左我成年了<br />\n<br />\n5.某教主(已故)<br />\n2符中金閃 776石寶3希望的影像:<br />\n<img src=\"http://i.imgur.com/qgsHEwI.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fi.imgur.com%2FqgsHEwI.jpg&h=7218de8f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n6.<strong>[black]衛宮士郎[/black]</strong><br />\n<img src=\"http://i.imgur.com/jlei43O.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fi.imgur.com%2Fjlei43O.jpg&h=44f6cb8c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"http://i.imgur.com/629zEfJ.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fi.imgur.com%2F629zEfJ.jpg&h=ddaffb41&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/x6Smf88.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fx6Smf88.jpg&h=e48926af&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n7.神父<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/09/28/020045_f369c7915e2491559958085e99d9c64e.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F09%2F28%2F020045_f369c7915e2491559958085e99d9c64e.png&h=ae681dfb&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"http://i.imgur.com/XwtVU7J.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fi.imgur.com%2FXwtVU7J.gif&h=3354fdcb&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"http://i.imgur.com/DvlgNi4.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fi.imgur.com%2FDvlgNi4.gif&h=9d71e588&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Cj3u1O5.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FCj3u1O5.jpg&h=fb3fb806&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/045EqRG.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F045EqRG.png&h=09d7c7d0&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"http://i.imgur.com/iErAqgb.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fi.imgur.com%2FiErAqgb.jpg&h=7dfd6eb2&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: gold;\">英靈靚相介紹:</span><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/07/25/114903_500514581c9b6d073fa3da4f3f5422e4.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F07%2F25%2F114903_500514581c9b6d073fa3da4f3f5422e4.jpg&h=f1404af4&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: gold;\">新手須知</span><br />\n連登apps台既fgo post係主要討論<span style=\"font-size: medium;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">日</span></span>ser<br />\n台服問題可免則免 <br />\n以下內容只適用於<span style=\"font-size: medium;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">日</span></span>ser<br />\n呢隻game三十石=十抽<br />\n課金就650hkd左右=167石<br />\n假如你想長玩 最符合效率就係<br />\n你可以先係淘寶買個首抽ac(顧名思義係全新ac但係有石)<br />\n大概四十蚊到 入面有幾十符+900幾石 <br />\n你冇睇錯只係四十蚊港紙左右<br />\n刷到有3-4個五星 就可以選擇開局<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/04/25/105223_d35d0be7c6a4d14c5d5602fe45279898.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F04%2F25%2F105223_d35d0be7c6a4d14c5d5602fe45279898.gif&h=0970a1ac&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/fight_connect.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><span style=\"color: gold;\"><strong>-催post專用環保post-</strong></span><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/fight_connect.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/524206/page/1\" target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/524206/page/1</a><br />\n<br />\n</div>"},{"pid":"2656923bfa96b233860cdcca91cf6cb4cf440fe7","tid":760000,"uid":68297,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-29T06:58:51.000Z","msg":"lm<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/wet.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"24aaaa15cb036f804c1bdb204ebacd88149cdebd","tid":760000,"uid":168942,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-29T06:58:53.000Z","msg":"lm"},{"pid":"4c1d2cb6b06b1cbe0b6f689fcca1fe5a5f496595","tid":760000,"uid":49275,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-29T06:58:53.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c73af177ace324f5bf942598a1ed474686744d43","tid":760000,"uid":13100,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-29T06:59:11.000Z","msg":"曬時間講啲開緊嘅活動<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f0fabe3ff5f003076b04223f1dd5e865a0d4bcb1","tid":760000,"uid":39020,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-29T06:59:14.000Z","msg":"pug<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3bf435a245bd6bb2c9e5ebd86f3aa0a89b2883c6","tid":760000,"uid":49275,"like":0,